title: convert_keras KeyError
body:
Hi I use Keras library and I'm trying to create onnx model.

    from keras.models import load_model
    model = load_model("model.h5")
  
    import onnx
    import onnxmltools
    onnx_model = onnxmltools.convert_keras(model, target_opset=7) 

and than I get this error
